room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by Xtreme Xscape in Portland
review: Super fun! Especially like the "competition" aspect of it... racing against the clock AND the other half of our party made it extra fun!

room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by Xtreme Xscape in Portland
review: We did the alien abduction room with 6 people and escaped! The staff was super friendly and fun. We had a good time. Definitely will think about coming in a bigger group for a competition next time.

room_title: Escape room "Alien Abduction" by Xtreme Xscape in Portland
review: We made a pit stop in Portland during our west coast vacation. During our stay, we ventured in to do an escape room- the alien abduction room was a challenge and so much fun. Great time had by all.
